Subject: Domain Block List  not working on Content
Description:
I have created a Content Aware Policy to block domains in the Domain Block List and applied it to web browsers, but it does not do anything.

no sure what I am doing wrong.
What_We_Know__c: - the customer created a Content Aware Policy to block domains in the Domain Block List and applied it to web browsers, but it does not do anything.
Solution_Comment__c: during the remote session we enabled Bypass DPI Certificate Rejection by Third-Party Applications which fixed the issue
